title: Linux Mint Debian Edition 6 “Faye” Is Now Available for Public Beta Testing
description:
Linux Mint Debian Edition (LMDE) 6 "Faye" distribution is now available for public beta testing based on Debian GNU/Linux 12 "Bookworm" and featuring the Cinnamon desktop environment.

title: TUXEDO Aura Linux Laptops Now Come with Wi-Fi 6E, LTE Modem, and TPM 2.0
description:
